text: The 2019 Seychelles First Division is the 40th season of Seychelles First Division, the top-tier football league in Seychelles. The season started on 9 March 2019.Seychelles 2019, RSSSF.com Due to transitional season, the teams are divided into two mini-leagues. There are no official overall champions. ==Mahé League== Some results are unknown and have been inferred. ==Inner- Island League== Some results are unknown and have been inferred. ==References== Category:Football leagues in Seychelles First Division Seychelles
